# Owner-employee payroll

## Pay runs (Supabase `payroll_runs`)

- Link each run to an `employee` record.
- Separate **employee withholdings** (income tax, RPC, AE, RQAP) from **employer contributions**.
- Net pay = gross − employee withholdings − other deductions.

## Remittances

- Track source deductions remitted to Revenu Québec / CRA outside the app (bank confirmations).
- Employer portions (RPC, AE, RQAP employeur) are additional cash outflows.

## Salary vs dividends

- Salary: payroll module with statutory deductions.
- Dividends: `dividends` table with equal split among active employees by default.
- Present trade-offs; owner confirms mix with CPA.

## Year-end

- Draft T4/RL-1 summaries from `payroll_runs` — CPA files.
